_sText:
I was just sitting here bored, so I decided that I would make my debut on FPSB and create something, so here it is, a bridge that took me a few hours to make, using quite a few different textures and the like.

Comes with a .vmf file for the actual prefab, and a .bsp incase you wanna play it ;). 

Warning: I didnt use any nodraws in the .bsp, so it may be a tad laggy, sorry about this :).
Thanks for checking it out =].
